'''New Hope Settlement''' was a small [[City/Legends|town]] on the [[Desert/Legends|desert]] [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Ladarra]]. As a failed colony with a reduced population, it was on the verge of becoming a ghost town; most of its buildings were boarded up and appeared to be abandoned.

The main street in downtown New Hope was flanked by stores and was where [[The Ellstree Bar]] was included.

